s:622:"<p>The Text and media area enables you to display text and multimedia on the course page.</p>

<p>You can use a Text and media area to:</p>

<ul>
<li>Split up a long list of course activities with a subheading or an image</li>
<li>Display an embedded video directly on the course page</li>
<li>Add a short description to a course section</li>
</ul>

<div class="helpdoclink"><a href="https://docs.moodle.org/501/en/mod/label/view" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><i class="icon fa fa-book fa-fw"></i>More help<i class="icon fa fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-fw ms-1" title="Opens in new window"></i></a></div>
";